{"lemma": "حَلْبٌ", "slug": "حَلْبٌ", "root": "ح.ل.ب", "root_slug": "ح-ل-ب", "root_link": "/words/roots/ح-ل-ب", "pos": "N", "pos_camel": "noun", "paradigm": [], "frequency_in_corpus": 0, "cross_references": {"qac": {"found": false}, "wiktextract": {"found": true, "entry_count": 7, "pos_tags": ["name", "noun", "verb"], "has_etymology": true, "sense_count": 11}, "lanes": {"found": true, "entry_ids": ["n8785", "n8790", "n8791", "n8792", "n8810"], "search_url": "https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AD%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%92%D8%A8%D9%8C"}}, "translations": {"en": "milking", "fa": "دوشیدن", "ur": "دودھ نکالنا", "tr": "sağım", "id": "memerah", "bn": "দুধ তোলা", "es": "ordeño", "fr": "traite", "de": "Melken", "ru": "доение", "zh": "挤奶"}, "definition": {"source": "wiktextract", "senses": [{"pos": "name", "gloss": "Aleppo (the capital city of Aleppo governorate, Syria)"}, {"pos": "name", "gloss": "Aleppo (a governorate of Syria)"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to milk"}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to yield milk", "tags": ["rare"]}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to grant milking, to assign an animal to milk", "tags": ["rare"]}, {"pos": "verb", "gloss": "to be black"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "verbal noun of حَلَبَ (ḥalaba) (form I)", "tags": ["form-of", "noun-from-verb"]}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "verbal noun of حَلِبَ (ḥaliba) (form I)", "tags": ["form-of", "noun-from-verb"]}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "fresh milk"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "Flueggea tinctoria; Euphorbia aegyptiaca and Euphorbia granulata"}, {"pos": "noun", "gloss": "Ḥalab, one of the tribes of Doms in Egypt", "tags": ["collective"]}]}, "etymology": {"source": "wiktextract", "text": "Perhaps from the root ح ل ب (ḥ l b), coming from the ancient tradition that Abraham gave milk to travelers as they moved throughout the region.\n\nCognate with Hebrew חלב (khaláv).\n\nRelated to the milk-giving qualities of these plants, compare the Spanish name of the spurge lechetrezna; but possibly from Classical Syriac, ܚܰܠܒ݂ܳܐ (ḥalbā, “milk”), construct state ܚܠܷܒ (ḥăleḇ), also meaning “spurge” in compounds."}, "ipa": ["/ħa.lab/"], "lanes_definition": {"source": "lanes", "entries": [{"entry_id": "n8785", "headword_ar": "حَلَبَ", "root": "Hlb", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, Mgh, Msb, K,) aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, Msb, K) and"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HalabN", "text_ar": "حَلَبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, A, Msb, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HalobN", "text_ar": "حَلْبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, Mgh, Msb, K) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HilaAbN", "text_ar": "حِلَابٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (K;) and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHtlb", "text_ar": "احتلب", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (S, K;)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He milked"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA) a she-camel (S, Mgh, Msb, TA) &c., (Msb,) a ewe, a she-goat, and a cow: (TA:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he drew forth the milk in the udder:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A, K: [see also 10:]) and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Halaba", "text_ar": "حَلَبَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "All~abana", "text_ar": "اللَّبَنَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he drew the milk from the udder"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. (S and K in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "rvA^", "text_ar": "رثا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", &c.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Halabota biAls~aAEidi AlA^a$ad~i", "text_ar": "حَلَبْتَ بِالسَّاعِدِ الاَشَدِّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Thou hast milked with the strongest fore arm"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] is a prov., meaning thou hast asked aid of him who will perform thine affair, or thy want: (TA:) or, accord. to A'Obeyd,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HalabotuhaA Alx", "text_ar": "حَلَبْتُهَا الخ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "I have milked her"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "&c., meaning I have taken it by force when I could not by gentle means. (TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$d", "text_ar": "شد"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Hulibato SaraAmi", "text_ar": "حُلِبَتْ صَرَامِ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,) or"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "SuraAmu", "text_ar": "صُرَامُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (S, and some copies of the K, in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Srm", "text_ar": "صرم"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "The last milk was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "has been drawn from the udder,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is another prov., used in a case when an evil has attained its crisis: (TA:) or it means (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the excuse reached,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "has reached, its utmost point:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(AO, S and K in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Srm", "text_ar": "صرم"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ":) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the she-camel that hah"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "little or"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "no milk was milked,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "has been milked;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "denoting a calamity. (IB, TA in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Srm", "text_ar": "صرم"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A_ino kunota", "text_ar": "اـِنْ كُنْتَ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "kaA*ibFA faHalabota qaAEidFA", "text_ar": "كَاذِبًا فَحَلَبْتَ قَاعِدًا"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "If thou lie, mayest thou milk sitting;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e., lose thy camels, and become an owner only of sheep or goats, and thus, after having milked camels standing, milk sheep or goats sitting: this, also, is a proverbial saying, like the following:"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "maA lahu Halaba qaAEidFA waA@SoTabaHa baAridFA", "text_ar": "مَا لَهُ حَلَبَ قَاعِدًا وَا@صْطَبَحَ بَارِدًا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "What aileth him?"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "May he"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[be reduced to]"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "milk"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a sheep or goat"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sitting, and drink cold"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "water, not hot milk. (TA.) And"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Halaba Ald~ahora A^a$oTurahu", "text_ar": "حَلَبَ الدَّهْرَ اَشْطُرَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He experienced good fortune and evil,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is another prov. (TA. [See this and other exs. in art."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "$Tr", "text_ar": "شطر"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".]) So, too,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "vum~a A^aqolaEato", "text_ar": "ثُمَّ اَقْلَعَتْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Halabato HalobatahaA", "text_ar": "حَلَبَتْ حَلْبَتَهَا", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA [but not there explained]) [lit."}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "She performed her act of milking,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "then desisted:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "but, as explained in Freytag's Arab. prov. (i. 343 and 281), meaning (assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(a cloud,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "saHaAbap", "text_ar": "سَحَابَة"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ",)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "sent forth a fine rain,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "then ceased:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and some read"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HalobapF", "text_ar": "حَلْبَةً"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "A^aHolabato", "text_ar": "اَحْلَبَتْ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", meaning the same: see another reading voce"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "jalaba", "text_ar": "جَلَبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]. ―         -b2-  [Hence,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Halabahu", "text_ar": "حَلَبَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(assumed tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He mulcted him:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "see an ex. voce"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "fa$~a", "text_ar": "فَشَّ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ": and see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HalabN", "text_ar": "حَلَبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ".] ―         -b3-  [Hence also,]"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Halaba", "text_ar": "حَلَبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (A, K,) aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (A,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HalobN", "text_ar": "حَلْبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,) (tropical:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He set himself upon his knees, in the posture of the milker:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(A:)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he sat on his knees;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K;) or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "on his knee: he sat on his knee"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "in eating, or in milking a ewe or she-goat:"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he kneeled."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(TA.) You say,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AuHolubo wakulo", "text_ar": "اُحْلُبْ وَكُلْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Kneel thou like the milker, and eat"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "]: (A:) it denotes a lowly [and becoming] mode of sitting while eating. (TA.)"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "layosa fiY kul~i HiynK A@Holubo", "text_ar": "لَيْسَ فِى كُلِّ حِينٍ ا@حْلُبْ"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faA@$orubo", "text_ar": "فَا@شْرُبْ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(tropical:)  ["}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Not at every time"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "is it said,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "kneel thou, and understand"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "] is a prov. applied in the case of anything that is forbidden, or denied: AA says that"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AlHlb", "text_ar": "الحلب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the act of kneeling;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Al$rb", "text_ar": "الشرب"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "the understanding"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a thing: and one says to a stupid person,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AuHolubo vum~a A@$orubo", "text_ar": "اُحْلُبْ ثُمَّ ا@شْرُبْ"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Kneel thou; then understand:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "one says also,"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "lys klu Hyn", "text_ar": "ليس كلُ حين"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHlb fA$rb", "text_ar": "احلب فاشرب"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "[in Freytag's Arab. Prov., ii. 437, thus:"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "faA^a$oraba", "text_ar": "فَاَشْرَبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "layosa kul~u HiynK A^aHolaba", "text_ar": "لَيْسَ كُلُّ حِينٍ اَحْلَبَ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", and explained as meaning"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Not every time permits to milk and then to drink:"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "i. e. not every time aids thee in performing a work; therefore thou shouldst act prudently, and not expend thy wealth without rule and measure.] (TA.)       -A2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Halaba Alr~ajula", "text_ar": "حَلَبَ الرَّجُلَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He milked for the man."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.) ―         -b2-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Halabahu", "text_ar": "حَلَبَهُ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "AHlbhu", "text_ar": "احلبهُ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "He assigned to him, to be milked by him,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "a ewe or she-goat, and a she-camel: (K:) or the latter,"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "he assigned to him what he should milk."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S.)       -A3-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HalabuwA", "text_ar": "حَلَبُوا"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (K,) aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", (TA,) inf. n."}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HalobN", "text_ar": "حَلْبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "and"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HuluwbN", "text_ar": "حُلُوبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "They assemble,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "collected themselves together, from every quarter."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K, TA.) [See also 4.]       -A4-"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "Haliba", "text_ar": "حَلِبَ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": ", aor."}, {"kind": "text", "text": ","}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "It"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(hair &c.)"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "was,"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "or"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "became, black."}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(K.)"}], "source_refs": ["S", "Mgh", "Msb", "K", "A", "TA"]}, {"entry_id": "n8790", "headword_ar": "حُلْبٌ", "root": "Hlb", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": ": see"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HulobapN", "text_ar": "حُلْبَةٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "."}], "source_refs": []}, {"entry_id": "n8791", "headword_ar": "حَلَبٌ", "root": "Hlb", "body": [{"kind": "text", "text": "is an inf. n.: (S, A, Msb, K: see 1:) ―         -b2-  and also signifies"}, {"kind": "italic_en", "text": "Milk drawn from the udder;"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "(S, A, * Mgh, K;) or so"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "libanN HalabN", "text_ar": "لِبَنٌ حَلَبٌ"}, {"kind": "text", "text": "; (Msb;) and so ↓"}, {"kind": "arabic", "text_bw": "HaliybN", "text_ar": "حَلِيبٌ", "orth_type": "arrow"}, {"kind"